===Noun===
{{en-noun|es}}

# Any of several [[shrub]]s or [[tree]]s of the [[family]] [[Rutaceae]].
# The [[fruit]] of such [[plant]]s, generally [[spherical]], [[oblate]], or [[prolate]], consisting of an outer [[glandular]] [[skin]] (called [[zest]]), an inner white skin (called [[pith]] or [[albedo]]), and generally between 8 and 16 [[sector]]s filled with [[pulp]] consisting of [[cell]]s with one end attached to the inner skin. Citrus fruits include [[orange]], [[grapefruit]], [[lemon]], [[lime]], and [[citron]].

